abindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sib1665702770803.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sib1665702770803.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sib1665702770803.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sib1665702770803\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"sib1665702770803__unifaceentity_422107\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This constructor is used to create an instance for an entity with specific types of fields.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"sib1665702770803__topic_d129164e1_d129165e1_d129166e1\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sib1665702770803_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sib1665702770803__codeblock_lgv_xnc_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">import com.rocketsoftware.uniface.jci.*;\n\nUnifaceEntity (int[] fieldTypes)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sib1665702770803__topic_d91562e1_d91563e1_d91564e1_d91565e1_d91566e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1200687e58\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sib1665702770803__p_d129170e1_d129171e1_d129172e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">fieldTypes</var>—an array containing\n            the types of each of the fields required. The array is numbered starting with zero,\n            which is an exception to the general Uniface convention.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Field Type Constants</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__1\">Constant </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__2\">Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__1\">UTYPE_STRING </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__2\">Uniface string </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__1\">\nUTYPE_BOOLEAN\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__2\">Uniface boolean </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__1\">UTYPE_NUMERIC </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__2\">Uniface numeric </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__1\">UTYPE_FLOAT </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__2\">Uniface float </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__1\">UTYPE_DATE </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__2\">Uniface date </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__1\">UTYPE_TIME </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__2\">Uniface time </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__1\">UTYPE_DATETIME </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__2\">Uniface date time </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__1\">UTYPE_RAW </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__2\">Uniface raw </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__1\">UTYPE_IMAGE </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sib1665702770803__table_d15347e1_d15348e1_d15349e1__entry__2\">Uniface image </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sib1665702770803__topic_d91567e1_d91568e1_d91569e1_d91570e1_d91571e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1200687e179\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sib1665702770803__p_d129176e1_d129177e1_d129178e1\">Returns an empty entity, that is, with no occurrences.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sib1665702770803__topic_d91572e1_d91573e1_d91574e1_d91575e1_d91576e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1200687e188\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sib1665702770803__p_d129182e1_d129183e1_d129184e1\">Uniface entities are usually returned through parameters in Uniface operations, but they can also be created from Java using this class. Use the <code class=\"ph codeph\">UnifaceEntity</code> class to:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sib1665702770803__li_d46484e1_d46485e1_d46486e1\">Get entity information, such as the number of fields and the current number of occurrences\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sib1665702770803__li_d46487e1_d46488e1_d46489e1\">Create new occurrences\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sib1665702770803__li_d46490e1_d46491e1_d46492e1\">Remove occurrences\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sib1665702770803__li_d46493e1_d46494e1_d46495e1\">Get data from and set data in fields of a specific occurrence\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sib1665702770803__p_d129185e1_d129186e1_d129187e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">UnifaceEntity</code> class is used to specify entity parameters from Java. The Java <code class=\"ph codeph\">UnifaceEntity</code> object is passed to Uniface as a Java object (<code class=\"ph codeph\">IN</code>), and from Uniface to Java as a Java object (<code class=\"ph codeph\">OUT</code>). The Java <code class=\"ph codeph\">UnifaceEntity</code> object is a local copy only.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"sib1665702770803__note_N100A5_N10063_N10016_N10001\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Occurrences are passed by value, not by reference. When entity data is\n            passed as an <code class=\"ph codeph\">IN</code> (or <code class=\"ph codeph\">INOUT</code> ) parameter, all occurrences\n            are considered new data. A subsequent <code class=\"ph codeph\">store</code> from ProcScript, therefore,\n            most likely leads to <code class=\"ph codeph\">duplicate key</code> errors.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sib1665702770803__topic_d91577e1_d91578e1_d91579e1_d91580e1_d91581e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1200687e249\">\n                       \n Methods\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sib1665702770803__li_d46496e1_d46497e1_d46498e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rxn1665702770939.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rxn1665702770939.html\" title=\"The createOccurrence method creates an occurrence.\">UnifaceEntity.createOccurrence</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sib1665702770803__li_d46499e1_d46500e1_d46501e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fbu1665702771008.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fbu1665702771008.html\" title=\"This method returns the type of a field.\">UnifaceEntity.getfieldType</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sib1665702770803__li_d46502e1_d46503e1_d46504e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gge1665702771076.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gge1665702771076.html\" title=\"This method retrievves the number of fields each occurrence has.\">UnifaceEntity.getNumberOfFields</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sib1665702770803__li_d46505e1_d46506e1_d46507e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tgq1665702771163.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tgq1665702771163.html\" title=\"This method retrieves the current number of occurrences in this entity.\">UnifaceEntity.getNumberOfOccurrences</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sib1665702770803__li_d46508e1_d46509e1_d46510e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bxj1665702771230.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bxj1665702771230.html\" title=\"Return the contents of the specified field as a Java object.\">UnifaceEntity.getOccurrenceField</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sib1665702770803__li_d46511e1_d46512e1_d46513e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ssj1665702771299.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ssj1665702771299.html\" title=\"Remove the specified occurrence from the set of occurrences.\">UnifaceEntity.removeOccurrence</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sib1665702770803__li_d46514e1_d46515e1_d46516e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zlz1665702771367.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zlz1665702771367.html\" title=\"This method removes all occurrences from an entity.\">UnifaceEntity.removeOccurrences</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sib1665702770803__li_d46517e1_d46518e1_d46519e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rup1665702771440.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rup1665702771440.html\" title=\"Insert new contents into the specified field.\">UnifaceEntity.setOccurrenceField</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sib1665702770803__li_d46520e1_d46521e1_d46522e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yuv1665702771510.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yuv1665702771510.html\" title=\"This method returns a string with the contents of the entity.\">UnifaceEntity.toString</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">To specify an entity named UE, with two fields, the first field of type String and the second of type Numeric, you would use the following code:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sib1665702770803_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sib1665702770803__codeblock_npm_c4c_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">int fieldTypes [] = new int [2];\nfieldTypes[0] = Values.UTYPE_STRING;\nfieldTypes[1] = Values.UTYPE_NUMERIC;\nUnifaceEntity UE = new UnifaceEntity(fieldTypes);\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"sib1665702770803__note_N10127_N10119_N100BC_N10016_N10001\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The <code class=\"ph codeph\">fieldTypes</code> array is numbered starting from\n               zero. This is an exception to the general Uniface convention. In addition,\n               non-database fields are not transported through the URB interface—if you need to\n               access an entity that contains non-database fields, you should omit them from the\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">fieldTypes</code> array.</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531991\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531991\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UnifaceEntity Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 This constructor is used to create an instance for an entity with specific types of fields. Explain this code import com.rocketsoftware.uniface.jci.*; UnifaceEntity (int[] fieldTypes) Copy Parameters fieldTypes —an array containing the types of each of the fields required. The array is numbered starting with zero, which is an exception to the general Uniface convention. Table 1. Field Type Constants Constant Meaning UTYPE_STRING Uniface string UTYPE_BOOLEAN Uniface boolean UTYPE_NUMERIC Uniface numeric UTYPE_FLOAT Uniface float UTYPE_DATE Uniface date UTYPE_TIME Uniface time UTYPE_DATETIME Uniface date time UTYPE_RAW Uniface raw UTYPE_IMAGE Uniface image Return Values Returns an empty entity, that is, with no occurrences. Description Uniface entities are usually returned through parameters in Uniface operations, but they can also be created from Java using this class. Use the UnifaceEntity class to: Get entity information, such as the number of fields and the current number of occurrences Create new occurrences Remove occurrences Get data from and set data in fields of a specific occurrence The UnifaceEntity class is used to specify entity parameters from Java. The Java UnifaceEntity object is passed to Uniface as a Java object ( IN ), and from Uniface to Java as a Java object ( OUT ). The Java UnifaceEntity object is a local copy only. Note: Occurrences are passed by value, not by reference. When entity data is passed as an IN (or INOUT ) parameter, all occurrences are considered new data. A subsequent store from ProcScript, therefore, most likely leads to duplicate key errors. Methods UnifaceEntity.createOccurrence UnifaceEntity.getfieldType UnifaceEntity.getNumberOfFields UnifaceEntity.getNumberOfOccurrences UnifaceEntity.getOccurrenceField UnifaceEntity.removeOccurrence UnifaceEntity.removeOccurrences UnifaceEntity.setOccurrenceField UnifaceEntity.toString To specify an entity named UE, with two fields, the first field of type String and the second of type Numeric, you would use the following code: Explain this code int fieldTypes [] = new int [2]; fieldTypes[0] = Values.UTYPE_STRING; fieldTypes[1] = Values.UTYPE_NUMERIC; UnifaceEntity UE = new UnifaceEntity(fieldTypes); Copy Note: The fieldTypes array is numbered starting from zero. This is an exception to the general Uniface convention. In addition, non-database fields are not transported through the URB interface—if you need to access an entity that contains non-database fields, you should omit them from the fieldTypes array. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}